Costs and quality of life of multiple sclerosis in Sweden.

Berg J(1), Lindgren P, Fredrikson S, Kobelt G.

Author information:
(1)Stockholm Health Economics, Stockholm, Sweden. jenny.b@healtheconomics.se

The study objective was to analyse the costs and quality of life (QOL) of 
